text: Necati is a Turkish given name for males. People named Necati include: * Necati "Neco" Arabaci (born 1972), Turkish businessman, criminal, and high- ranking member of the Hells Angels * Necati Ateş (born 1980), Turkish footballer * Necati Çelim (1909–1986), Turkish politician * Necati Er (born 1997), Turkish athlete * Necati Cumalı (1921–2001), Turkish writer * Necati Şaşmaz (born 1971), Turkish actor * Necati Zontul, Turkish torture and rape victim ==See also== * Nejat (disambiguation) Category:Turkish masculine given names
title: Necati
